trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> or an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref>, specifying the individual MIME formats for the parts of the HTTP transmission.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta un elemento extensibility aggiunto a un <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"> </xref> o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"> </xref>, singoli MIME dei formati per le parti della trasmissione HTTP.
Questa classe non può essere ereditata.

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni su come specificare i protocolli per i servizi Web XML, vedere [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni sui servizi descrizione linguaggio WSDL (Web), vedere la specifica http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of extensibility elements added to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref> to specify the MIME format for the parts of the MIME message.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene la raccolta di elementi di estendibilità aggiunti il <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"> </xref> per specificare il formato MIME per le parti del messaggio MIME.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"></xref> representing extensibility elements added to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection"> </xref> che rappresenta gli elementi di estendibilità aggiunti per il <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"> </xref>.
